author: Tyler McCarthy
title: Actor Mark Blum dead at 69 due to coronavirus complications
description: Actor Mark Blum, known for his work in theater as well as in films “Desperately Seeking Susan,” “Crocodile Dundee” and the Netflix series “You,” died at age 69 reportedly due to complications from the coronavirus.
